reviews.review_text: china doll jerry solo  like pelling a onion  back till gets to the middle and take you out the room  sends shivers down my spine  no wonder  he takes a nether 10 minutes wind down  gets better with playing  in the band  i miss this  one the band ditch me  they had go to north east  to do it  i loved  85  jerry in red  the rooster  wasent  to lazy to crow  that year
